# This directory holds fitted-weights output from scripts/training/fit_logit.py.
#
# Files:
#   v2.json           — production fitted weights (commit when n_races >= 200
#                       from real BEL/SAR/AQU corpus)
#   _features.jsonl   — feature extractor intermediate output (gitignored)
#   _*.jsonl          — any other scratch JSONL files (gitignored)
#
# Until the first real fit is produced, this directory is intentionally empty.
# The RailbirdFittedWeights IIFE in index.html handles a 404 on v2.json
# gracefully: v2 scoring silently falls back to DEFAULT_V2_WEIGHTS.
